snippet.title: Gematombe - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Gematombe is a competitive action block puzzler that calls back to classic games such as Arkanoid, Puzzle Bobble, Breakout, Puyo-Puy, Touhou, and more. Featuring a wide array of characters with different abilities, 60 levels with multiple modes, humorous cut scenes, and more. Gematombe is available now on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Nintendo Switch.
